*nix style daemon template
===========================================================

This project sets up the basic infrastructure to write a
daemon on a unix-style system. All of the preparation work
is contained in the template including setting up syslog.

References to note:

Linux Daemon Writing HOWTO
http://www.netzmafia.de/skripten/unix/linux-daemon-howto.html

Unix Daemon Server Programming
http://www.enderunix.org/docs/eng/daemon.php


